      "content": "Hey, I'm doing a paper for my psych history class on the eugenics movement in the early 1900s. Can you elaborate on the specific arguments that eugenicists used at the time to justify their ideas about racial hierarchies? Like, what was their \"scientific\" reasoning for ranking different groups?",
