      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's really helpful for the \"ranking\" section of my paper. I'm trying to understand the exact logic they used to claim these differences were actually hereditary and not just social. For example, how did they use things like IQ testing or skull measurements (craniometry) back then to scientifically \"prove\" that these higher-ranked groups were more evolved or intellectually advanced than the groups at the bottom? I want to capture their specific logic for the assignment.",
